commitResults.messageBody:
Bugs Discovered:
1. EditModuleCommand class did not have a "equal" method.
2. Link class did not have a "isSameLink" method (which determines equality by only comparing link contents).
3. Link class "equal" method (which should determine equality by comparing both link and name) did not compare names.
